An '''Initiate''' (also called '''Savant'''), was the lowest rank of the [[Shaper caste]]. They would be taken and trained in [[Primary Shaping]] as crechelings and young adults, until they were taken on by a [[Master Shaper]]. Once their training was complete, they would be declared [[Shaper Adept]]s, though they would often continue working with their Masters.

